Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,[eyecatch]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,[ed]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 1057 "Bad Guys"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[op]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:05.60,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see yesterday's episode of Yaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:06.48,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.50,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,A whole bunch of Kamen Yaibas showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:11.07,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know whoâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:12.48,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:20.08,Kaori,SIGN LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Hirasawa Kaori (27) \NWife
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:20.08,Seiko,SIGN RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Hirasawa Seiko (68) \NMother-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:32.91,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.14,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.28,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.18,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.10,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.72,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.54,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Who were those brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:48.86,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.84,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those old ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:55.67,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't thieves. We're the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:00:59.24,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:00.54,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:06.50,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, are you really more concerned \Nabout the rug than our injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.80,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:13.01,Ryoji,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Hirasawa Ryoji (31) \NSon-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:17.40,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm very concerned about your injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:22.46,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Son-in-law, hurry up and bring \Nthe first-aid box and treat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.68,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:25.95,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:27.52,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:33.14,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:35.59,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.72,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:43.54,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:46.14,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Must be tough being their son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:49.76,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious clouds block your field of view!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.41,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Clear them away with deductive \Nreasoning and the sky sparkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.45,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A mother, a daughter, and a timid man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:55.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,From within their family, a case grows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.01,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:48.99,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(399,1)}Bad Guys
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.49,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Bad Guys!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:53.62,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man. I've been in a terrible \Nmood since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.13,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's a quirk of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:01.95,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The entire day might end \Nup being terrible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:05.39,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,What? That would be super terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.89,Supako,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Supa-ko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:20.15,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Hirasawas' son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.70,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.51,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.32,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,People were gossiping about \Nthem in my neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.28,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Gossiping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.50,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The Hirasawas used to own \Na lot of land around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.20,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They still own the Hirasawa Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.29,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hirasawa Apartments,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.33,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,the Hirasawa Parking Lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.65,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,and Hirasawa Farms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.55,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They're a rich family that owns \Na bunch of other properties, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.17,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Their son-in-law originally worked
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.86,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,at an insurance company that did a \Nlot of business with the Hirasawas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:58.06,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,He married their only daughter \Nafter a formal meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:02.94,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,At first people said he \Nwas after their money,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:06.70,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,but they still treat him like a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.09,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.30,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.56,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.81,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.56,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I'm so sorry to make you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.18,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he keep apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.85,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,All he's holding is a single leek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.74,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Cut him some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.07,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.82,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.96,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.39,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.56,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.77,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,How far did you go to get groceries?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.34,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:08.49,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Son-in-law, do the laundry \Nbefore making dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.07,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to clean, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.76,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.57,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.82,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and start dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.56,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.48,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go jogging now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.56,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.85,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:24.79,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:27.24,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What an inconsiderate son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.04,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get everything \Ndone by the time we come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:33.74,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.81,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure the curry's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.70,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.55,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Make mine extra spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.75,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.49,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.58,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Call emergency services and the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.94,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,1-1-9.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.09,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I need one firetruck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.62,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Firetruck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.51,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, one ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.09,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go tell the son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:13.70,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.95,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency, Mr. Son-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:09.63,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you kids are the witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.94,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.51,Pamphlet,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,For a Secure Future \NToto Life Insurance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Insurance pamphlets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:04.47,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Their son-in-law originally worked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.23,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,at an insurance company that did a \Nlot of business with the Hirasawas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:13.40,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,He married their only daughter \Nafter a formal meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:18.28,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,At first people said he \Nwas after their money,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:22.29,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,but they still treat him like a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.66,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The insurance company that does business \Nwith the Hirasawas caused the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.47,DCMain,KINUE,0000,0000,0000,,How are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.83,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.95,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to pretend the \Naccident didn't happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.44,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,At first, people said he \Nwas after their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.23,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The Hirasawa family's fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:34.00,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,H-How are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.34,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. You're asking \Nabout Hirasawa Kaori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.90,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:42.01,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,And her mother Seiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:42.88,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:48.45,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them experienced a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.23,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,But because the paramedics \Ndid such a good job
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.44,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,and the accident was reported quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.15,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,we were able to do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:59.29,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,That said, they're not out of the woods yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.90,DCMain,DOCTOR,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to continue \Nobserving their progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:20.01,Kinue,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(438,146)}Hasegawa Kinue (31) \NA Beautiful Woman
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:53.72,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.83,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That lady was trying to remove her IV tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.50,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.09,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.15,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.35,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.96,DCMain,KONOE,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to remove her IV tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:23.63,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time to close your \Neyes and analyze your own behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:27.88,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you closing your eyes so \Nyou can reflect your actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.33,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're closing your eyes and dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:36.62,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of the day the Hirasawa \Nfamily fortune is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.30,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.84,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,You were eavesdropping on our \Nconversation, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:55.48,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,You never should have come here, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.48,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to do this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.57,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:06.93,DCMain,NURSE B,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.94,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:09.94,DCMain,NURSE A,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.12,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:16.20,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. The professor's performing \Nmaintenance on my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.83,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.41,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to trip me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.63,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so desperate to play with \Na ball, then I'll play with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.02,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.77,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.87,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:42.19,DCItalic,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, are you really more concerned \Nabout the rug than our injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.83,DCItalic,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.78,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:50.32,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Brand name track suits are so comfy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.77,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,These accessories are so striking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:53.58,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.94,DCMain,KAORI,0000,0000,0000,,This should be good enough for \Nrestaurants that have a dress code.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:58.83,DCMain,SEIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:04.95,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't an accident, but a \Ncrime committed by the son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.64,DCMain,NURSE A,0000,0000,0000,,What was his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:11.82,DCMain,NURSE B,0000,0000,0000,,She's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.77,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.03,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.47,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.42,DCMain,KINUE,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.82,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kinue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.32,DCMain,KONOE,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:00.24,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,So Conan-kun went after \Nthe culprit's black car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.06,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.18,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't heard from him yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.34,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:08.08,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to wait for Hirasawa \NSeiko-san and Kaori-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.57,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,to wake up so I can gather \Ninformation from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.55,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.28,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's the black car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.54,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun must be at this hospital, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:36.85,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.18,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Genta, Mitsuhiko, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.53,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Call the police immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.79,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi is right here next to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:48.79,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:52.74,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The Hirasawa family's son-in-law and \Na woman from the insurance company
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.72,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,are working together to seize \Nthe Hirasawa family fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.74,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They need to be arrested immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.24,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.50,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're inside some dirty sheets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.92,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a laundry cart in \Nthe first floor hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.81,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.83,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a chime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.01,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's an elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.00,DCMain,KINUE,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.35,DCMain,RYOJI,0000,0000,0000,,To the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.90,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.46,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,A man and woman believed to be the culprits
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:38.41,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,have kidnapped a young boy \Nand are heading to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,They probably intend to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.92,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:44.83,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.16,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.14,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Genta, Mitsuhiko, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.12,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.12,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun, do you hear that? Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.68,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.44,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi, Genta, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:38.10,DCMain,KONOE,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoji, the police are down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:42.26,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.45,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.76,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:50.66,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Damn these sheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.94,DCMain,RESCUE SQUAD,0000,0000,0000,,We've recovered the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.77,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.90,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.12,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.83,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.68,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.04,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.38,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.30,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:06.94,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.06,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:32.08,Hospital,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Beika General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:13.97,DCMain,RESCUE SQUAD,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we'd like to pack up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:15.91,DCMain,RESCUE LEADER,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Leave them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.34,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun, what was it like \Nto fall from the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:51.57,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been scary, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:53.49,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It was terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:56.76,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,But you looked really cool \Nflying through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:57.52,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:59.54,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to try flying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.11,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:02.79,DCMain,RESCUE CAPTAIN,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:03.52,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:05.78,DCMain,RESCUE CAPTAIN,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:09.10,DCMain,RESCUE CAPTAIN,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:11.60,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.03,DCMain,RSECUE CAPTAIN,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:18.32,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You worked real hard, hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.54,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:22.87,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:28.05,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys. You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.57,DCMain,RESCUE CAPTAIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:36.56,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.52,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,The cushion's flat as a pancake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:24:09.05,DCEpPreview,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.87,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The time is 17:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:51.96,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki Yosuke, you're under arrest \Nfor the murder of Odawara Shuhei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:56.53,DCMain,KATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:59.79,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,After knocking out the \Nvictim with a metal pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:02.04,DCMain,KATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:07.32,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what that was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:08.66,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:15.05,DCNextEp,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,The Man Who Camped Out at the Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:13.78,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is "The Man \NWho Camped Out at the Police Station!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:34.99,Hint,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Window
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.38,0:24:33.14,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:34.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A window pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:39.99,Don'tMiss,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:36.40,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's a big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.40,0:24:37.26,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.26,0:24:37.79,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.79,0:24:39.45,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Give me a break, guys.
